The Disciplinary Committee shall before taking any disciplinary action—
(a) give the member at least fourteen days' notice of the time and place of the proceedings;
give the member at least fourteen days' notice of the time and place of the proceedings;
(b) serve the member with the notice in compliance with this Act;
